      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a good start for the outline. Can you actually write out a couple of paragraphs for the introduction and the first point? I want it to sound really authoritative, like it's an undeniable moral and economic necessity, not just one way of looking at it. Use strong language to make the reader realize that the current system is basically rigged.",
